    B --> C[For each О»: train on K-1 folds\nvalidate on 1 fold вҶ’ average error]
    C --> D[Pick О»* with lowest CV error]
    D --> E{Apply 1-SE Rule?}
    E -->|Yes вҖ” simpler model| F[Pick largest О» within\n1 std error of minimum]
    E -->|No| G[Use О»* directly]
