    B -->|Yes| C[Linear SVM]
    B -->|No / Unknown| D{How many features?}
    D -->|p >> n  e.g. text| E[Linear SVM\nor Lasso + Logistic]
    D -->|p вүҲ n or p < n| F[RBF Kernel SVM\ntune C and Оі]
    D -->|Known polynomial\ninteractions| G[Polynomial Kernel\ntune d, Оі, r]
    C & E & F & G --> H[GridSearchCV on C + kernel params]
