## 16. SVM for Regression (SVR)

SVR fits a **tube of width $2\varepsilon$** around predictions вҖ” points inside the tube have zero loss.

$$\min_{\mathbf{w}}\; \frac{1}{2}\|\mathbf{w}\|^2 + C\sum_{i}(\xi_i + \xi_i^*)$$

